8. Be3
{ This offers a favorable transposition to the 6. . .. c5 line, but Black has tried a variety of other moves. }
8... c5
{ This transposes to an inferior line given in 6... c5 where the Knight is better placed on c6 than d7. Our continuation was f4 with a good game. }
