[SetUp "1"]

1. Qf3
{ Not all tactical theme problems are tactical wins! Sometimes you have to see tactics that maintain the White advantage. This is such a thematic move for White it needs the additional reinforcement of showing up in a tactical theme. The point here is that   1...dxc3  will cost Black his Queen after  2.Nxg7+  Kf8  3.Nxe6+  . Black needs to respond with   1...Qd7  when further tactical possibilities are coming per the coverage in the theoretical section  2.Bg5  would be White's next move. }
*

